	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />If you want to see source code to better understand how the NES works, and troubleshoot issues in your own emulator, look at the source code to Nintendulator.
<br />Its PPU code is a great reference to what events happen on which PPU cycle.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


